    {{#> case/paragraphe title="The challenge" }}
        <p>15% of H&M online customers are not members of the loyalty program.
            How might we encourage them to sign up?</p>
    {{/case/paragraphe}}

    {{#> case/paragraphe title="My role" }}
        <p><strong>Product Designer</strong> in a new Team in charge of increasing the number of sign ups.
        </p>
    {{/case/paragraphe}}

    {{#> case/paragraphe title="The process" }}
        <p>We were bombarded with requests to add features, or put the sign up button
            in more places. But there was little data to back that up! So, I started by conducting research
            to inform our decisions.</p>

